==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ld.
<hw>Ld.</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The abbreviation for
<altname>limited</altname>, term appended to the name of a company that
is organized to give its owners limited liability; also abbreviated
<altname>Ltd.</altname> It corresponds to <altname>Inc.</altname> in the
United States.</def> <mark>[Chiefly British]</mark> <mark>[abbr.]</mark>
⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> limited company, Ltd.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

